it acts on the current hunk in a Magit buffer instead of on
a position in a file-visiting buffer.

(fn &optional WHOAMI FILE-NAME OTHER-WINDOW)" t)
(autoload 'magit-add-change-log-entry-other-window "magit-extras" "\
